title: The Moment I Knew (Taylor's Version)
description:
This was the defining moment in Taylor's relationship when she saw it for what is was.. It's the moment that she knew it was over, and she has referenced it in several songs. Lacey, Ana, Amy and Nick break down the story of the saddest birthday party ever.
What did we miss? What would you like to hear? There are lots of ways to reach us!
